title: We Quiz Each Other To See If We Are Actually Experts In the Subjects We Claim We Are
description: We all claim to be experts in certain subjects, Dave with the 80s, Falen with pop culture, Jenny with math, and Tina with Disney.  We quiz each other in the subjects and 3 of us prove to be experts, one, not so much.
